name: Mammoth evolution
description:
The mammoth is a species of extinct elephant, one of the many species that make up the order of trunked mammals called the proboscideans.  and there are repeats of mammoths in other galaxies, these mammoths are remade into robots contested by two tribes on a desert planet, Desert planets, also known as dry planets, arid planets, or sand planets, are a type of theoretical terrestrial planet with a similar surface consistency.  with hot deserts on Earth.  there are only two tribes.

sci-fi movement conceptually. Inspiration by sci-fi 80s vibes like bruce pennington, Moebius (Jean Giraud) H.R GIGER And many more.

Illustrated by ink digital 2022
